room_title: Escape room "French Quarter House of Curiosities" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
room_address: 830 Union Street Suite 101 New Orleans, LA 70112
room_description: Arriving at the French Quarter House of Curiosities to meet your friend Selma, the door unexpectedly locks behind you. What’s going on in this innocent little shop? Where is Selma? And what is the weird shop owner keeping hidden in the back room? Unravel the secrets of the Curio Shop before the stars align and you find yourself stuck in the shop forever – or worse!
